content: Hi! The library team page on the rust-lang website links to a stream that doesn't exist for the Library API team, t-libs-api
Is this stream yet to be created, or does it actually exist under a different name?
maybe it was an overzealous search and replace ? probably good to ask in the t-libs stream https://rust-lang.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/219381-t-libs
I think we want to just keep using T-libs, or perhaps make a T-libs/api stream.
